Introduction

ATTI is a British K-pop girl group consisting of three members. They independently debuted on October 6, 2023, with their EP titled Peaches. Notably, all three members were previously part of the first British-based K-pop girl group, KAACHI, which disbanded under FrontRow Records in February 2023.
